title: 820-3476 ALL_SYS_PWRGD 0V
message:
Remove Q8150 and test again.
If still low, remove PGOOD resistors R8164-69, one by one, until ALL_SYS_PWRGD goes high.
Keep in place R8167.

title: 820-3476 ALL_SYS_PWRGD 0V
message: Nevermind, reballed SMC and board now boots, thanks for guidance!
